Firstly, wow, what a great emulator. The skins are simply fantastic as well. Thanks for your work.

Secondly, is there plans to include the TI89Titanium? I did a quick google but found no information on this.

Glad you like the program. Unfortunately there are no plans to include the TI-89 as it uses a completely different processor then the 8X series. If you're looking for a good 89Ti emulator i suggest the TIEmu, which does all the 68k calcs.

Thanks for the answer. This is somthing I should have looked up.. I have tried tiemu which seems rather adequate.
